changeset:   1697:a8d5f5bca1aa
tag:         tip
user:        Trevor Williams <phase1geo@users.sourceforge.net>
date:        Tue Jan 12 01:13:46 2016 -0600
files:       lib/edit.tcl lib/indent.tcl lib/menus.tcl lib/multicursor.tcl lib/snippets.tcl lib/version.tcl lib/vim.tcl
description:
* Adding support for <<, >>, #<<, #>> Vim commands.
* Fixing cursor position for indent and unindent operations to be located at the beginning of the first word of the line.
* Lots of internal changes to better document variable types.
* Adding support for :set shiftwidth=# Vim command.
* Fixing a few bugs in Vim word cursor movement operations.
* Fixing indent/unindent space usage (uses Editor/IndentSpaces or shiftwidth value instead of only two spaces).
* Removing partial shiftround and softtabstop Vim command support.


